      'The watch-enthusiast turning point came in 2018 with the full-metal stainless GMW-B5000, which reimagined the 1983 square in steel and pulled serious collectors into the fold for the first time. Since then the analog-digital GA-2100 "CasiOak" became a runaway 2019 hit and meme-worthy bestseller, while the top-tier MR-G line — hand-finished titanium with sapphire and Japanese craft techniques like tsuiki hammering — cemented G-Shock\'s claim to genuine luxury at four-to-five-figure prices.',
